Author: comfortbun
Text: i’m stuck in the same cycle sis. binging is personally a spur of the moment thing which makes it so fucking difficult to combat. any type of stress, small or large, triggers my vulnerability and causes me to run frantically under the comfort of food. i wish an empty stomach had the same effect on me lol.   i’m seeing a psychiatrist in a few weeks and was thinking of bribing binging up during the session. apparently there are certain pills that can help with the urges. i’d look into it
